metadata.description: Buying dogi will be the best decision you have made this year, 1/ The founder is from a top VC on Wall Street and has a close relationship with a celebrity on Twitter. 2/ Roadmap, Musk will change to dogi's avatar in a week. 3/ We will accept $200 million from Wall Street in a month. 4/ In two months we will follow Musk into space.
